C:\Users\aayoa\Desktop\aries-cli\ORI.md:143:- **Cache prefix discipline.** Everything above `CACHE_PREFIX_BREAK` in `src/prompt.ts` is cached daily. Nothing dynamic (dates, git state, per-turn data) may sit above it.
