C:\Users\aayoa\Desktop\aries-cli\RUNNING.md-168-- **Tool-result disk spillover**: large results write to disk, model gets path + preview. Conversation never accumulates noise.
C:\Users\aayoa\Desktop\aries-cli\RUNNING.md-169-- **Five compaction strategies** layered: tool-result budget → history snip → microcompact → context collapse → autocompact. Snip (keep head/tail, drop middle) is cheap and we don't do it.
C:\Users\aayoa\Desktop\aries-cli\RUNNING.md-170-- **Subagent architecture**: YAML frontmatter agent definitions, own tool allowlist, own context. Parent only sees synthesis.
